Class ExpressionTree<E>

java.lang.Object
Problems
BinaryTree<E>
ExpressionTree<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, ProblemInterface
public class ExpressionTree<E>
extends BinaryTree<E>
In this class we give the constructor a statement and from this statement we generate a prefix or postfix tree. We evaluate these trees by using the evaluate methods we have defined in the previous assignment.
